'''Cravers''' were the subject of a common galactic expression. To "throw someone to the cravers" was to abandon them. [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] stated to [[Borsk Fey'lya]] that "...five minutes ago you were ready to throw [[Garm Bel Iblis/Legends|Bel Iblis]] to the '''cravers''' if it would buy you enough time to bring in the [[Katana fleet]]."

